I choosed these studies because I like their issues, it allows me to work in different sectors that I appreciate. For example journalism or evenemential. I like those sectors because of people who works in those. For me these people are able to do a lot of things and I want to be like them. They work hard to have results but in sectors that they like so, I think, for them, it’s not really work but it’s long pleasure. For me this is important to have a work in a sector that I like so I choosed these studies because I like their issues and all people I saw working in those sectors liked their jobs. I also saw concerned and motivated people in these sectors so for me it’s a good thing because it allows to work with people who appreciate their jobs and it also allows to work more efficiently. A happy person is more efficient than a sad person. And for the rest of the team it’s more interesting to work with people who smile because they like their jobs
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the produced data
